DECK ARTICLE &#8211; Open Format (or Standard Format &#8211; see &#8216;Final Word&#8217; for changes)<br />
TITLE: Pipe Dreams in Moria<br />
<br />
Starting Fellowship:<br />
The One Ring, Isildur&#8217;s Bane<br />
Frodo, Old Bilbo&#8217;s Heir<br />
<a href="javascript:card_browser(35)">Gimli, Son of Gloin</a><br />
<a href="javascript:card_browser(874)">Merry, Friend to Sam</a><br />
<br />
Site Path:<br />
1.	The Riddermark (Pull Aragorn)<br />
2.	Uruk Camp (Anti Uruk&#8217;s)<br />
3.	Barrows of Edoras (Increase chance of pipes + swarm)<br />
4.	Ered Nimrais (Anit large fellowships)<br />
5.	Helms Gate (good for my orcs)<br />
6.	Hornburg <a href="javascript:card_browser(303)">Armor</a>y (I have a lot possessions)<br />
7.	Hornburn Wall (good for swarm)<br />
8.	Wizards Vale (no much other choice)<br />
9.	Palantir Champber (if the have any burden&#8217;s then its my last ditch to overwhelm them)<br />
<br />
